Minor ward
Discworld ritual help
Major ward


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Minor ward -- places a protective rune on an object
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Minor ward places a rune on an object.  The rune will go off when
a person tries to steal the object, doing no damage but allowing you 
to identify the thief.  You need a holy symbol to perform this ritual.
.EP

